✨WE SOLD OUR NEW HOUSE!!! READ⬇️ FOR STORY:

After two years of moving across the country and living in this new home here in South Carolina and after a spending a small fortune on a huge kitchen, living room, and laundry room remodel...

The most beautiful land was privately offered to us this spring. So we bought 5 acres in the country, sold our custom home in a gated community, and moved into a rental while we are building in the country off a dirt road. 😁👏🏼 I can’t believe this is happening!

My dreams of homesteading, beekeeping, and riding horses have become a reality and life is sooo good!

Still focusing on my health but I think I’m turning a corner and will share more when I’m ready. Thanks for your love and support over the years!🫶🏼🩷

Josh and the kids are doing awesome! And our little Gracie too.🐶 We are so happy here...and here for good. The Adams definitely belong in The South!

I didn’t get to share much of this last home yet but after the holidays, I’ll be sharing lots of before and afters on the blog.

Life is short, my friends! Find a way to make your dreams a reality! ✨🩷✨🩷✨🩷✨🩷✨
